gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 132, Wizards 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeat the Wizards, 132-102.  OG Anunoby (26 points, six rebounds), Pascal Siakam (22 points, six rebounds, 11 assists) and Scottie Barnes (20 points, 12 rebounds, eight assists) combine for 68 in the victory, while Kyle Kuzma (14 points, four rebounds, seven assists) and Jordan Poole (14 points, four rebounds, four assists) combine for 28 for the Wizards in the losing effort.  The Raptors improve to 12-18 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 5-25.
